tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE qualitative_researchers (researcher_id INT, researcher_name VARCHAR(50), research_field VARCHAR(50), research_topic VARCHAR(100));
CREATE TABLE data_models (model_id INT, model_name VARCHAR(50), model_description TEXT, model_version DECIMAL(5, 2));
CREATE TABLE data_queries (query_id INT, query_name VARCHAR(50), query_description TEXT, query_params JSON);

CREATE TABLE project_comments (
    comment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    commenter_name VARCHAR(255),
    comment_text TEXT,
    comment_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE participants (
    participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_name TEXT,
    age INT,
    study_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (study_id) REFERENCES studies (study_id)
);

CREATE TABLE data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_id INT,
    study_id INT,
    data_values JSONB,
    FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES participants (participant_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (study_id) REFERENCES studies (study_id)
);
